Package: dyLMM
Title: Dyadic Linear Mixed Models
Version: 0.0.0.9001
Author: John Sakaluk <jksakaluk@gmail.com>
Maintainer: John Sakaluk <jksakaluk@gmail.com>
Description: Fitting dyadic linear mixed models (LMM/MLM/HLM) including ICC models
    and actor-partner interdependence models (APIM) for indistinguishable and
    distinguishable dyads. Interoperates with dySEM and dySim.
